cover the following third-party components, which retain their own licenses:

이 MIT 라이선스는 본 저장소의 FLOW 패키징 스크립트(installer/, about.html,
screenshots/, README, 설정)에만 적용됩니다. 다음 제3자 구성요소는 각자의
라이선스를 따릅니다:

1. Microsoft Sysinternals ZoomIt
   - License: Microsoft Sysinternals Software License
   - URL: https://learn.microsoft.com/sysinternals/license-terms
   - This repository does NOT redistribute the ZoomIt binary. The online
     installer downloads it directly from Microsoft Sysinternals Live
     (https://live.sysinternals.com/ZoomIt64.exe) at install time.

2. Naver Nanum Fonts (나눔글꼴)
   - License: SIL Open Font License / Naver Free-Use License
   - URL: https://hangeul.naver.com/font
   - Already pre-installed on most Korean Windows installations; this
     installer only references the font by name in registry, not the
     font files themselves.
